              <li>Thakur Dalpat Sengar — 1857 freedom fighter</li>
              <li>Mardansingh Sengar — Etawah chief (18th c.)</li>
              <li>Kali Prasad Sengar — Banda estates</li>
              <li>Harcharan Sengar — Mughal-era feudatory</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="clan-data-block">
            <h4>Military Traditions</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Famous for sword-fighting and cavalry warfare</li>
              <li>Controlled key Yamuna river crossings militarily</li>
              <li>Supplied forces to Peshwa campaigns in Bundelkhand</li>
