              <li>Ramaite devotion — deep Vaishnava-Shaiva synthesis</li>
              <li>Patron of Hanuman and Durga temples</li>
              <li>Maintained Sanskrit gurukuls in Etawah region</li>
              <li>Clan deity: Devi Vindhyavasini and Kali</li>
